HEADWORD: Inoculable
<hw>In*oc"u*la*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Inoculate</er>.]</ety> <def>Capable of being inoculated; capable of
communicating disease, or of being communicated, by
inoculation.</def>⟦br⟧
